data.description:
Welcome to 2119 Mountain Lake Rd, a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Dallas, TX. This lovely residence features a spacious living room, perfect for both relaxation and entertainment.

As you arrive, you'll be greeted by the convenience of a 7-car carport cover, offering ample parking for your vehicles and guests.

The property is conveniently located, providing the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and urban convenience. Residents will appreciate the easy access to the bustling downtown area, with its array of cultural attractions, dining hotspots, and vibrant entertainment options

With its inviting interior and desirable amenities, this home offers a wonderful opportunity for comfortable living in a vibrant community.

Don't miss the chance to make this delightful property your new home
